Olympic road race\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 334}, {\"ngram\": \"theTour de France\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The most logical choice.\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 401, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"The most logical choice\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It ensures that I have a little more time and thus can prepare longer and better,\\\" Van der Poel said Wednesday.\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little more time\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 443}, {\"ngram\": \"Van der Poel\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van der Poel already had a start position for the Olympic mountain bike race, and was keen to make up for his costly crash that knocked him out of the running in the Tokyo Olympic Games in 2021.\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 709, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van der Poel\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"a start position\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic mountain bike race\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"his costly crash\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"the running\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympic Games\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet once he saw a favorable road race course in and around Paris, he made the call that the best chance for success for an elusive Olympic gold medal would be focusing 100 percent for the road race.\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 770, \"end\": 775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 7.042956556783477e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a favorable road race course\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 755}, {\"ngram\": \"the call\", \"from\": 785, \"t