ing and focus in what's been a highly successful season racing in the world champion's rainbow jersey.\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1357, \"end\": 1371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rainbow_jersey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"rainbow jersey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rainbow_jersey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rainbow_jersey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The decision\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"his training\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"a highly successful season racing\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van der Poel lit up the spring classics, with huge wins at E3 Saxo Classic, Tour of Flanders and Paris-Roubaix, a podium at Li\\u00e8ge-Bastogne-Li\\u00e8ge, as well as top-10s at Milan-San Remo and Gent-Wevelgem.\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1471, \"end\": 1484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"score\": 0.9816675037644488, \"rank\": 0.004431782209560121, \"text\": \"Paris-Roubaix\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\"}, {\"begin\": 1542, \"end\": 1556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\\u2013San_Remo\", \"score\": 0.9637570188426524, \"rank\": 0.008209745762714191, \"text\": \"Milan-San Remo\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\\u2013San_Remo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\\u2013San_Remo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van der Poel\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"the spring classics\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"huge wins\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"E3 Saxo Classic\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1448}, {