rectly played a bit of a role.\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fact\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2386}, {\"ngram\": \"the rainbow jersey\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2435}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2463}, {\"ngram\": \"a role\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a special year.\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a special year\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As world champion I like to ride in that jersey as much as possible.\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"world champion\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2513}, {\"ngram\": \"that jersey\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I also prefer not to miss the Tour de France.\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2598, \"end\": 2612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.100814293301855e-12, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that proved to be a good preparation last year, then towards the World Championships.\\\"\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2704, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good preparation\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2654}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van der Poel is one of the most prolific, multi-disciplined riders of the modern era.\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Poel\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2718}, {\"ngram\": \"the most prolific, multi-disciplined riders\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2772}, {\"ngram\": \"the modern era\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A six-time world champion in